{"tid":682891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭博：日本味之素考慮出售淘大食品","createTime":"2018-05-29T08:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T09:25:49.000Z","uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2938a55606f9d47e5d9260de83a695a5a0c9b275","tid":682891,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:32:47.000Z","msg":"Ajinomoto Mulls Sale of Hong Kong's No. 1 Soy Sauce Brand <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-05-28/ajinomoto-is-said-to-weigh-sale-of-chinese-soy-sauce-brand-amoy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2018-05-28%2Fajinomoto-is-said-to-weigh-sale-of-chinese-soy-sauce-brand-amoy&d=Z8UvfzV38QS9GCWS0GEfHYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=91fd1348\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-05-28/ajinomoto-is-said-to-weigh-sale-of-chinese-soy-sauce-brand-amoy</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://invest.hket.com/article/2082678/%E5%82%B3%E5%91%B3%E4%B9%8B%E7%B4%A0%E6%B4%BD%E5%94%AE%E6%B7%98%E5%A4%A7%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finvest.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2082678%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%2591%25B3%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E6%25B4%25BD%25E5%2594%25AE%25E6%25B7%2598%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%2593%2581%2Furl%5D&d=Z8UvfzV38QS9GCWS0GEfHYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=78bb2498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://invest.hket.com/article/2082678/%E5%82%B3%E5%91%B3%E4%B9%8B%E7%B4%A0%E6%B4%BD%E5%94%AE%E6%B7%98%E5%A4%A7%E9%A3%9F%E5%93%81/url]</a><br />\n2018年5月29日 09:39 星期二<br />\n傳味之素洽售淘大食品 <br />\n<br />\n《彭博》引述消息人士報道，日本企業味之素正考慮出售本港醬油品牌淘大食品。味之素正與顧問合作評估潛在買家的興趣。惟潛在出售仍於初部階段，味之素可能決定保留業務。據悉估計出售金額介乎7,000萬至8,000萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，亞洲私募股權公司Unitas Capital正在尋求以6億美元出售另一家中國調味品生產商─嘉豪食品，潛在買家包括荷美爾食品公司。<br />\n<br />\n淘大食品是香港著名品牌，已有110年歷史。味之素在2006年以約18億港元（相當於2.35億美元）收購淘大。淘大去年在本港市場的市佔率達36%，但仍未躋身中國5大品牌。市場預計，至2022年，中國醬油市場的規模將達862億人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《傳聞》味之素擬售中國醬油品牌淘大食品<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/rumours_detail.php?newsid=ETR280529376\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Frumours_detail.php%3Fnewsid%3DETR280529376&d=Z8UvfzV38QS9GCWS0GEfHYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=455e8795\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/rumours_detail.php?newsid=ETR280529376</a> <br />\n經濟日報 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fcaf59f92302d488a5aec9887e142371b56c1bf","tid":682891,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:35:24.000Z","msg":"日本同香港豉油有乜分別"},{"pid":"2463bda690cbee08d3c4cdc420d02d3dd5c6332d","tid":682891,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:39:14.000Z","msg":"支那接受"},{"pid":"313641c9f3670bcbef6f2cc2aeeb38ba793623ae","tid":682891,"uid":13503,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:41:07.000Z","msg":"淘大真係垃圾無樣嘢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565dcfed1407dd92c45b9efb686dc25cc52f59e2","tid":682891,"uid":174601,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:41:46.000Z","msg":"淘大去年在本港市場的市佔率達36%，但仍未躋身中國5大品牌。<br />\n<br />\n記者個腦係咪入咗水<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵佢考通識一定肥"},{"pid":"03cae75647d3609220744f68a5151165c5df1028","tid":682891,"uid":25841,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"313641c9f3670bcbef6f2cc2aeeb38ba793623ae","tid":682891,"uid":13503,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T08:41:07.000Z"